column2: Men's 2023 College Basketball Tournament Bracket Data

column16: 2024 Game Information will populate once available!

column18:
This sheet uses the importrange function to pull in 
data from a master data source. If you find the function
isn't recalculating quick enough, simply reload your spreadsheet.

Scores for live games will be shown if available but teams won't advance until the game is over.

To view the raw data source go here:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DyuuT9zPSh9RdzrAF_1bY6HhyuYKckL3E6wr-sGKZTs/

To pull in individual game data
function, see the TedTournament() custom function here:
https://github.com/TedJuch/TedTournament

TedTournament() function is preloaded on this template.
